      • addReplacement

        public static void addReplacement(java.lang.String pkg,
                  int id,
                  java.lang.Object replacement)
        Add a new resource replacement.
        Internal use only.
        Parameters:
        pkg - The package whose resource we want to replace, null for system.
        id - The id of the resource.
        replacement - The replacement object, its type depends on
        the resource being replaced. Can also be a forwarder.
        See Also:
        ElPollo.Resources, ElPollo.Resources.Forwarder
